OL,5, After seven years running Italy's      
OL,6, flagship museum the Uffizi, its        
OL,7, director has clearly had enough of     
OL,8, inappropriate punctuation.             
OL,10,FEike Schmidt has laid out his rules for
OL,11,Femail etiquette in a message to staff. 
OL,13,FBold characters are out, although      
OL,14,Funderlining is still acceptable where  
OL,15,Fsuitable for words or salient phrases. 
OL,17,F"You should also avoid whole sentences 
OL,18,Fin capitals," Mr Schmidt says.         
